flowchart LR
    IN[3-lane block input] --> DEMUX[Deinterleave x0 / x1 / x2]
    DEMUX --> E0[Phase branch E0]
    DEMUX --> E1[Phase branch E1]
    DEMUX --> E2[Phase branch E2]
    E0 --> FFA[Shared L3 FFA recombine]
    E1 --> FFA
    E2 --> FFA
    FFA --> QS[Round / Saturate]
    QS --> OUT[3-lane output]
